        ## Getting started
        
        ### Tests:
        
        ```
        docker-compose run --rm web python manage.py test
        ```
        
        ### Run example app
        
        ```
        docker-compose up
        ```
        
        ### Run integration tests:
        
        ```
        python3 
        
        >> from gurutools.integration import plays
        ```
        
